{"tid":2318882,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"暗黑界健身AV全裸超辣！爆肥20公斤「偶像時期舊照」曝","createTime":"2020-12-09T16:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T17:04:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48a291bb574ecac16d90f14647ff34c932c395e5","tid":2318882,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"闖入暗黑界的寫真女星七海緹娜(七海ティナ)，今年27歲的她原本過去以古屋偶像身分出道，隨後轉行當寫真女星，並於同年加入成人AV團體「惠比壽麝香葡萄」，隨後正式從成人界出道成為AV女優，因為迷上健身的關係，身材變得相當健美，甚至還參加健美比賽得獎！近日七海緹娜曝光了自己偶像時舊照，立刻掀起網路一片熱議！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/09/2927575-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F09%2F2927575-PH.jpg&h=96b66e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲七海緹娜是健身級AV女優。（圖／翻攝自tinaaaaa1208推特）<br />\n<br />\n練就一身健美身材的七海緹娜以「肌肉系列」打出知名度，除了上圍相當豐滿外，一身精壯肌肉更讓人過目難忘，到現在還是經常透過健身來訓練自己，也時常參加健身比賽。不過在開始健身前，其實過去七海緹娜在偶像時期的身材，和現在有相當大的落差，幾乎就像是完全不同的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/09/2927581-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F09%2F2927581-PH.jpg&h=54fb82ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼七海緹娜曬出她超勵志的胖妹時期舊照。（圖／翻攝自tinaaaaa1208推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/09/2927580-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F09%2F2927580-PH.jpg&h=95755d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在名古屋偶像時期的七海緹娜，無論臉蛋和身材大腿都頗為臃腫，造成五官也不突出，更經常擺出一副厭世眼神，隨後轉行當寫真明星後，也是面臨被嫌胖的問題，因此讓她痛下決心透過運動健身、調整飲食減肥。與過去剛出道時相比，竟整整瘦了20公斤，體態明顯不一樣了外，後來她甚至靠健美肌肉闖出名號。<br />\n<br />\n七海緹娜更於推特曬出自己的健美比賽照，相當樂於享受現在的生活。事實上，先前她曾透露媽媽與家人並不認同她作為一個AV女優的身分，不過仍相當支持她做自己喜歡的事情，讓她忍不住直呼「自己真的很幸福。」"},{"pid":"1128788f0296582d8f72eda3570ddc44e8c2388a","tid":2318882,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/09/2927588-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F09%2F2927588-PH.jpg&h=2fb6bc2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼七海緹娜現在不但瘦了20公斤，更參加健美比賽得獎。（圖／翻攝自tinaaaaa1208推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/09/2927582-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F09%2F2927582-PH.jpg&h=cd19e4aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94625a023ab6f7d67fbb4a2f0b99154402a48dfe","tid":2318882,"uid":57461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"Seed"},{"pid":"acea7e6530d4f753fcb833027a76891475769fb7","tid":2318882,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476b354da3440f85c8b03ea56f4e1c40f5202f30","tid":2318882,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2cf76edac0a5a2e2a44be83d7e8a814acb6575","tid":2318882,"uid":206466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:18:54.000Z","msg":"素顏小小恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ad2b5c85227224f1fca9162e81b0ee7ebba4cc","tid":2318882,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T16:24:07.000Z","msg":"法官大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a30512b608bd83fd0b813febba95ce4aab49c7","tid":2318882,"uid":16659,"like":0,"disli